*MiscPanel: (11x1, Id datetime, Title "13:42 Jun 15")
*MiscPanel: (2x1, Title "|")
*MiscPanel: (3x1, Title "85%")
*MiscPanel: (3x1, Title "  ", Font "xft:NotoSans Nerd Font:pixelsize=17")
