#
# Music Panel
#
DestroyModuleConfig MusicPanel:*
Style MusicPanel NoHandles
*MusicPanel: Columns 6
*MusicPanel: Rows 5
*MusicPanel: Colorset 1
*MusicPanel: (6x1, Id artistname, Title "No Song", Frame 0)
*MusicPanel: (6x1, Id songname, Title "Playing", Frame 0)
*MusicPanel: (6x1, Id songtime, Title "0:00 \- 0:00", Frame 0)
*MusicPanel: (2x1, Title Prev,\
  Action (Mouse 1) "Exec exec playerctl previous")
*MusicPanel: (2x1, Title Pause,\
  Action (Mouse 1) "Exec exec playerctl play-pause")
*MusicPanel: (2x1, Title Next,\
  Action (Mouse 1) "Exec exec playerctl next")
*MusicPanel: (3x1, Id shuffle, Title Shuffle,\
  Action (Mouse 1) "Exec exec toggle-shuffle")
*MusicPanel: (3x1, Id loop, Title Loop,\
  Action (Mouse 1) "Exec exec toggle-loop")

#
# Audio Panel
#
DestroyModuleConfig AudioPanel:*
Style AudioPanel NoHandles
*AudioPanel: Columns 4
*AudioPanel: Rows 2
*AudioPanel: Colorset 1 
*AudioPanel: (1x1, Id vol, Title 95%, Frame 0)
*AudioPanel: (1x1, Title X)
*AudioPanel: (1x1, Title --,\
  Action (Mouse 1) "Exec exec changevol -2")
*AudioPanel: (1x1, Title ++,\
  Action (Mouse 1) "Exec exec changevol +2")
*AudioPanel: (2x1, id micmute Title "Mic Mute",\
  Action (Mouse 1) "Exec exec micmute")
*AudioPanel: (2x1, Title Mixer,\
  Action (Mouse 1) "Exec exec pavucontrol")


# 
# Workspace Panel
#
# TODO: can likely refactor this by appling multiple rules to all elements
DestroyModuleConfig WorkspacePanel:*
Style WorkspacePanel NoHandles
*WorkspacePanel: Columns 4
*WorkspacePanel: Rows 1
*WorkspacePanel: Font "xft:azukifontBI:pixelsize=17"
*WorkspacePanel: (1x1, Id desk0, Title "0", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 0, \
              ActiveColorset 1, Colorset 1, Frame 0)
*WorkspacePanel: (1x1, Id desk1, Title "1", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 1, \
              ActiveColorset 1, Colorset 0, Frame 0)
*WorkspacePanel: (1x1, Id desk2, Title "2", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 2, \
              ActiveColorset 1, Colorset 0, Frame 0)
*WorkspacePanel: (1x1, Id desk3, Title "3", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 3, \
              ActiveColorset 1, Colorset 0, Frame 0)

DestroyFunc ChangeDesk
AddToFunc   ChangeDesk
+ I SendToModule FvwmButtons ChangeButton desk0 Colorset 0
+ I SendToModule FvwmButtons ChangeButton desk1 Colorset 0
+ I SendToModule FvwmButtons ChangeButton desk2 Colorset 0
+ I SendToModule FvwmButtons ChangeButton desk3 Colorset 0
+ I SendToModule FvwmButtons ChangeButton desk$0 Colorset 1

DestroyModuleConfig EventNewDesk:*
*EventNewDesk: PassID
*EventNewDesk: new_desk ChangeDesk

#
# Date Panel
#
DestroyModuleConfig DatePanel:*
Style DatePanel NoHandles
*DatePanel: Columns 1
*DatePanel: Rows 1
*DatePanel: (1x1, Swallow DateTime 'Module FvwmScript datetime.script', Frame 0)

#
# Task Bar / FVWM Icon Man
#

DestroyMenu MenuIconOps
AddToMenu   MenuIconOps
+ "(De)Iconify"         Iconify
+ "(Un)Maximize"        Maximize
+ "(Un)Shade"           WindowShade
+ "(Un)Sticky"		Stick
+ "(No)TitleBar"	Pick (CirculateHit) ToggleTitle
+ "Send To Desk"        Popup MenuSendToDesk
+ "" Nop
+ "Close"               Close
+ "Destroy"             Destroy
+ "" Nop
+ "Raise"		Raise
+ "Lower"		Lower
+ "" Nop
+ "StaysOnTop"          Pick (CirculateHit) Layer 0 6
+ "StaysPut"            Pick (CirculateHit) Layer 0 4
+ "StaysOnBottom"       Pick (CirculateHit) Layer 0 2
+ "" Nop
+ "Identify"            Module FvwmIdent

DestroyFunc IconManClick
AddToFunc   IconManClick
+ I ThisWindow (Raised, !Shaded, !Iconic, CurrentPage) Iconify
+ I TestRc (Match) Break
+ I ThisWindow (!Raised) Raise
+ I ThisWindow (Shaded) WindowShade
+ I ThisWindow (Iconic) Iconify
+ I ThisWindow (AcceptsFocus) FlipFocus

DestroyModuleConfig FvwmIconMan:*
Style FvwmIconMan NoHandles
*FvwmIconMan: ManagerGeometry 1x0-5+5
*FvwmIconMan: ButtonGeometry 120x30+490-5
*FvwmIconMan: UseWinList true
*FvwmIconMan: Colorset 1
#*FvwmIconMan: FocusColorset 1
#*FvwmIconMan: FocusAndSelectColorset 12
#*FvwmIconMan: SelectColorset 12
#*FvwmIconMan: IconAndSelectColorset 12
*FvwmIconMan: ReliefThickness 1
*FvwmIconMan: DrawIcons false
*FvwmIconMan: Format "%t"
*FvwmIconMan: Action Mouse 1 A sendcommand IconManClick
*FvwmIconMan: Action Mouse 2 A sendcommand Nop
*FvwmIconMan: Action Mouse 3 A sendcommand "Menu MenuIconOps"
*FvwmIconMan: Resolution global
*FvwmIconMan: Sort id
